quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,"O you shrouded<i class=""s"">(in your mantle) </i>—"
  74,2,"stand up and warn!"
  74,3,"And your<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>Lord glorify!"
  74,4,"And your<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>clothes purify!"
  74,5,"And abominations forsake<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>!"
  74,6,"And show<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>no favor, seeking self-gain!"
  74,7,"And to your<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>Lord endure patiently!"
  74,8,"So when the Trumpet is blown,"
  74,9,"that day will be a difficult day"
  74,10,"for the deniers—not easy."
